import urllib.request, urllib.parse
import re

def google_image_search(search, start):
    try:
        u = f"http://images.google.com/images?q={urllib.parse.quote(search)}{urllib.parse.quote(start)}"
        url = urllib.request.Request(u, headers={"User-Agent": "Mozilla/4.76"})
        response = urllib.request.urlopen(url)
        text = response.read().decode()
        response.close()
        if "\n" in text:
            text = text.replace("\n", "")
        array = re.findall(r'href=\"/imgres\?imgurl=([^\"]+)', text)
        google_images = [s for s in array if s.startswith("http://") or s.startsWith("https://")]
        return google_images
    except Exception as ex4:
        pass
